xmx1024
=======

Sample Codes for my blog site http://xmx1024.blogspot.com/

-----------------------------------------------------------------
~> mvn clean package

Run Jetty
~> mvn jetty:run
~> mvn jetty :run -DskipTests=true

Run Tomcat
~> mvn tomcat:run
or
~> mvn tomcat:run -DskipTests=true

Point your browser to the following URL:
    http://localhost:8080/xmx1024/

-----------------------------------------------------------------
Compile Metadata

If you're running this within an IDE, the metadata files need to be generated.
You should execute a compile first to generate these files.

~> mvn compile

You will then see metadata java source files used by JPA for type-safe queries
under this folder:
    target/generated-sources/apt
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Miscellaneous Notes

The database runs in-memory so it will be cleared each time you run jetty or tomcat.
